Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我們還有一個月時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你需要把書寫完  -沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我負責婚禮籌備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺時間過得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實很快  朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三周半之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的書終于寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的編輯喜歡新的結局  -你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概喜歡百分98.5吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已經接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠也不會完全滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太焦慮了  關鍵問題試試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經打了"完結"  準備暑假發行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這意味著我們應該吃次正餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,26美元一位  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我外婆的教堂朋友們能找到方法去吃自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們以前干過  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備好談談婚禮的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  我真是喜歡看你弄清單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經給婚慶公司訂金了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕和DJ都確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給供應商和客人都發郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒他們馬拉松在這周末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以交通狀況會不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你巧舌如簧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳娜確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮服在運輸途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續說點開放性問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你來說點開放性問題吧  -我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮前一天我們分開睡還是一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一起  肯定的  -同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經宣誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有史以來我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按時完成寫作任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次沒有按時完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們還需要再做一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜蜜的過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡座位卡上都是心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是三年級小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定你不想邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多人加入彩排晚餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡不需要動她書的錢  我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想弄小點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你想弄大一號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恰恰不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興能夠與瑪貝拉酒店永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}#佩特拉·瑪貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}#永遠熱情好客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在談談時間安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雞尾酒會是5點到6點  然后是晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚宴時  我們開始敬酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也會敬酒  -是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  而且還會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但佩特拉并不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但是她很激動  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她停頓的時候笑一笑吧  -我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非她當眾開除某人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮服合身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美  琳娜選的很準
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等不及想看你穿禮服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛你  家里見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了你的郵件  我們愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你給我們的靈魂證婚  不過我們認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這更像是婚禮之后私下的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實希望和你談點別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了拉斐爾的生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友們  看來最后的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終還是會被揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所想象的  或者是我想象的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事可以有很多種結局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到拉斐爾的父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結局可能是戲劇性的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是黑社會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能令人震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿絲不是他的母親  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者看似平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的父母曾經是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他們去世了  -當然  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一種完全不同的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我能找到的關于他們的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該由你來告訴拉斐爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我給你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你得帶一件更暖的外套  希爾瑪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷了我會去買的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紐約有地方逛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}確保我聯系你時你不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我可聽不出區別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}好呀寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特奧在哪兒  我得回家和拉斐爾談談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在樓上  他說他在給我準備一個大驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特奧  你干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拆了你的包裹  這樣你就不用搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來簡的兒子也不喜歡離別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特奧  親愛的  外婆還是得搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的  因為外公的事業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以外公不得不離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但外婆可以和我們呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  我不能  親愛的  -是的  你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是不想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是這樣的  -你要是想的話當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  馬特奧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們說好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎  我們每晚都會視頻通話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的感受  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你們怎么才來  -我們有點小問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們好多了  對吧笑瞇瞇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我能和你們一起睡在床上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不公平  如果他可以  那么我們也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是  別大吵大鬧的  馬特奧  -說夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的決定是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽你們的  -太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚睡覺的時候別這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里  你是個出色的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了吸引注意力  電視臺在秋季播出前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發布了《這是火星》的線上試播集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信它終于在美國開播了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們正在觀看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得會受歡迎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#火星這個標簽火起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國果然是愛我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像大家愛的是宇航局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一輛火星車在火星著陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你打包  換個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這令人很激動  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來可期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易莎找到我父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  但我不知道除了直說以外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能怎么告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們死于車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們住在意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們擁有一家面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是這樣  -面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太平凡無奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜我大概是在期待一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂劇的情節
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更瘋狂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道現在是得知這件事的最差時機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟馬上就要舉辦婚禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上  現在是最佳時機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在幾個月前  我可能會很絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我現在所能想到的全部就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擁有多少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實被家人環繞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我除了感激之外還能有何感受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛晃一槍  但畢竟箭在弦上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迫不及待地想嫁給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就帶我們來到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  走快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘們  回去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特奧  你怎么脫了褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好  只是彩排而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}為什么沒人把這當回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這已經是第三次走過場了  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}羅格里奧的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  我的帥小伙兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在婚禮上朗誦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你可要好好練習聲音的投射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓位置不好的觀眾也能聽到你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}行了  我們結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你寫誓詞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就寫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出版社這周要印刷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那本書的試閱本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送去給作家們評論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但等等  這還不是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一位作家是伊莎貝爾·阿連德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}著名女作家  代表作《幽靈之家》  被譽為"穿裙子的加西亞·馬爾克斯"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾·阿連德也許會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫一段我書背后的簡介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳娜  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  抱歉  我挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莎貝拉什么的  耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我本來打算等到婚禮結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再告訴你的  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我懷孕啦  -天哪  恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪個姐妹給你的卵子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明顯是更好看的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亞歷克西斯嗎  -是杰姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就這意思  我一直搞混她倆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真為你感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你這個超幸運的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該滔滔不絕地發表一些關于你的感言了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準確來說  她還真這么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都覺得我和四個姐姐一起長大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事實上  我有五個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我只喜歡其中一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  你對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我在這個世界上最佩服的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我長大后想成為你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是  在晚年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為簡的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這輩子最大的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話是真的  并且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  我也很開心我會有個兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  拉斐爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能叫我一聲爸爸  我將不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會搞明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  今晚大家也哭哭啼啼這么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我覺得也是時候來一點歡笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都知道簡很著迷于婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她上班時總是和番茄醬結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐爾  他一直都...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的襯衫太緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他的褲子...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  佩特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必要說的很搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是為了不像這樣激動才寫了這些笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得好像這樣沒效果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是太喜歡你們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愛情正是我所渴望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在祝你們一切幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺真是太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我通常不會祝別人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我愛你  -我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想說一段祝酒詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我經歷了一段艱難的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不小心讓你受孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想趁此時機說...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單地說  那天晚上  充滿了愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上  簡突然意識到了一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又有那種表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想去寫作嗎  -很快就好  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-當然  去吧  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來你為愛哽咽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  維蘭紐瓦的事就是會讓人們哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們就是為此而打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在這
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來有人被這些祝酒詞激發了靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  我不會告訴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的作家妻子  抄襲了她自己的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在寫我的結婚誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是突然想到了該怎么寫書的結尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我就能達到100%了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后發給我的編輯  看她能不能及時將文件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送去打印店  然后再拿給伊莎貝爾·阿連德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來打算今晚晚點再寫我的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的  人們常說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡著截止時間交的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該回去了  要上甜點了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定吃了太多蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很難過  我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是讓拉斐爾為難了  但也是出于好心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格里奧  不是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要給你說件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我不會搬去紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  你不能搬去紐約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想離開我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我一直在試著將這種感覺放到一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來支持你  但是我真的認為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說  這不是正確的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的護校學習
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才剛剛順利開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生活終于回到了正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須得走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我簽了一份合同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們能經常來往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作日我會住在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了周末  我們會去輪流看望彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮一下吧  反正你的時間很長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用在周中你拍戲的時候來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣通勤會讓你幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  羅格里奧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫完了我的婚禮誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那事我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  是我反應過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的書非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不擔心該怎么寫我的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很清楚我想說些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能每天和你在一起都是多么的幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常期待我們的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我對我們的未來感到非常興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這不像是我從小到大所看的肥皂劇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮并不是結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的故事才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我有點脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚你告訴我  我的生父母去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這并沒有讓我感到慌亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對一個人來講真的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因為我等不及未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跳過這個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就別等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們直接去度蜜月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  最終我們要大肆揮霍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們從來沒去度過假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在航班還有酒店預定上有一百萬個積分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們幾乎不用花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉身回了家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外婆叫我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不打算走是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考慮過了  這不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說  我不該顛倒我的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是二十世紀五十年代了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直想上衛校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改變主意了  我想待在這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為馬特奧把你嚇壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個孩子  媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不想我就不用去  我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想待在這見證一些事  比如你的書出版了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有晚餐  生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你被嚇壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我四十六歲了  我這一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都生活在你身邊  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這輩子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會想起我們的簡并不喜歡結局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在呢  就這么結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她從她媽媽身上遺傳的品質
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}它會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}那才是可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但如果我能來到這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}重新再來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你肯定會在紐約做同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}被嚇到也沒關系  希爾瑪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}讓恐懼再影響到我們的生活可就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會和我一起去紐約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  我太榮幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你這個  為了明天的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是條  項鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒打算戴什么首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是新娘套索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一條墨西哥式婚禮念珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮的時候  親友們把它繞到新郎新娘身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是結合的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親把它給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在  我想把它傳給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時  我想道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓你因為叫我爸爸這些事而感到為難
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們現在是在私下里  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是什么張嘴就來的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}九百六十萬粉絲  五萬五千三百八十二人正在關注
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  我火了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}一千二百七十萬粉絲  五萬五千三百八十二人正在關注
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,線上有事發生  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友們  這時他才意識到...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的粉絲量在暴漲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經雙倍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  變成三倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說人們肯定在看《這是火星》試播集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許就是現在了  拉斐爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能在美國走紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這事我們暫且保密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想搶了簡的風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明天就要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們共度的最后一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你們倆別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}明天可是簡的大喜之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}該睡覺咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰忘記關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可是我大喜的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要搬走了  心里難過著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我來關
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛你喲  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}這是我在你受洗那天讀的講稿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你可以在簡的受洗儀式上讀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}畫出十字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深深感受到了屋里充滿的關愛與支持
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友們  曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有這樣的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.78,0:25:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可惜  那一刻已經過去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:25:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我眼里...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.85,0:26:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  我的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.53,0:26:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的準新娘  新婚快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.15,0:26:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據預定計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發型師和化妝師應該就快...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.42,0:26:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們正好來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.84,0:26:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的編輯及時收到你的更改內容了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  不過這不重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.07,0:26:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會在正式印刷時換過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.09,0:26:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可伊莎貝爾·阿連德呢  她不肯看你的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定能做些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能親手把U盤
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送到印刷廠了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.52,0:26:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然不會在新婚之日去送
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.00,0:26:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.08,0:26:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不打算今天跑去經歷什么奇遇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.29,0:26:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們祭壇上見
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.18,0:26:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.09,0:26:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.28,0:26:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她或許沒這打算
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.91,0:26:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可看起來他有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.33,0:26:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎  有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.14,0:26:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}蒂莫西與湯普森出版社
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.79,0:26:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:27:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止出版
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.01,0:27:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都這樣說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.13,0:27:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十年代才這么說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.71,0:27:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請您幫個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.91,0:27:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三十分鐘后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.63,0:27:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多謝了  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.03,0:27:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你幫了我大忙了  -不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.08,0:27:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-祝你好運  兄弟  -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.68,0:27:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.21,0:27:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.00,0:27:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來簡得花大錢賠那道門了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.10,0:27:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  準老公
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.34,0:27:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  我進展順利
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.16,0:28:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的計劃可能要有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.06,0:28:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被抓了  得有人把我保釋出來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.89,0:28:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到家庭故事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.85,0:28:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個故事將經常被談起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.49,0:28:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他開車沖過了那道門
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.12,0:28:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被抓了  我得去把他保出來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.23,0:28:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可老媽開走了車去接喬治了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.21,0:28:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再叫輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.53,0:28:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  簡  我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.55,0:28:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-今天是你的婚禮  -所以必須我去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.74,0:28:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉弗真是太浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.22,0:28:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須是我去接他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.18,0:28:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.16,0:28:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能出什么問題
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.95,0:28:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}十分種路程
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.68,0:28:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟件上說你離我十分種路程遠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都過去二十分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.39,0:28:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為馬拉松比賽  我過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.43,0:28:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在普利茅斯街上車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.43,0:28:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離你只有幾個街區遠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.19,0:28:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.68,0:28:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.43,0:29:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.54,0:29:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.99,0:29:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭發真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.87,0:29:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.96,0:29:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.52,0:29:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.82,0:29:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-別停下  -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.92,0:29:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}司機已取消行程
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.57,0:29:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.06,0:29:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.81,0:29:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是巧合還是一場巨大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.21,0:29:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上車吧  簡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.01,0:29:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}還有十五站
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  有沒有什么辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能直接繞路
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.61,0:29:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.05,0:29:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長這么大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還不知道什么是公交車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.05,0:29:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.30,0:29:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我的未婚夫經歷了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.89,0:29:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外人工授精  綁架  邪惡雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起死回生的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.16,0:29:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們最后的障礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.16,0:30:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  能幫幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.86,0:30:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.85,0:30:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意用五千塊租下整輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來簡終于決定怎么揮霍這筆錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.92,0:30:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要給我們多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.13,0:30:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每人五十
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.18,0:30:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有事要做  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.21,0:30:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去銀行  干洗店
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.86,0:30:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-美甲店  -二百
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.24,0:30:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再多了  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.21,0:30:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮56分鐘后就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.38,0:30:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.84,0:30:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.40,0:30:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.06,0:30:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在哪兒  我們等著你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就過去  我接到新郎了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:30:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發短信告訴你上車的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.61,0:30:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開什么車  夠大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對夠大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.64,0:31:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓一讓
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓簡·格洛瑞娜·維蘭紐瓦的婚禮團過去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.05,0:31:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護婚紗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.27,0:31:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友們  就在這時
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是羅格里奧·維嘉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.52,0:31:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛播的那部《這是火星》
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.62,0:31:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.77,0:31:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  你很搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.04,0:31:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.97,0:31:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格里奧·維嘉  美國影星
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.17,0:31:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就是了  朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.34,0:31:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提前嘗鮮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.23,0:31:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來[轉型]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.05,0:31:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.79,0:31:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.25,0:31:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.23,0:31:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  我們到了  你們在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.41,0:31:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.41,0:31:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.30,0:31:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人  你站在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.23,0:31:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  能站在這里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.07,0:32:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也別看  轉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.51,0:32:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}站進來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但把裙子提起來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.59,0:32:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅燈停車了  把眼線筆給我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.25,0:32:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在后面怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.36,0:32:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.28,0:32:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.20,0:32:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.84,0:32:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.63,0:32:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}離婚禮還有0分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.94,0:32:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下我們真遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.24,0:32:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別緊張  你們沒到  他們不會開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.13,0:32:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我當新郎的時候也緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.88,0:32:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是三次  但誰記著這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.53,0:32:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們會完婚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會幸福美滿地在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.09,0:32:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不總是美滿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.00,0:32:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時  會遇到不順的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.32,0:32:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們會吵架  會急得跺腳
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.47,0:32:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我會急得跺腳
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.92,0:32:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們會熬過困境
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.02,0:32:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你們會有很多快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.79,0:32:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.96,0:32:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.25,0:32:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:33:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格里奧很好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.58,0:33:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.67,0:33:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸氣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.37,0:33:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都放輕松
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.93,0:33:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}婚禮已過六分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.37,0:33:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新郎新娘隨時會到
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.91,0:33:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我有一些笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.26,0:33:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在彩排晚宴上沒機會說
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.83,0:33:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰現在想聽聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.25,0:33:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不想  以后也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.71,0:33:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.50,0:33:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.63,0:33:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶  我沒準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是新娘簡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.49,0:33:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她真美
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.53,0:33:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么來了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.43,0:33:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐爾打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.73,0:33:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.37,0:33:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我說你對我還有感覺 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.84,0:33:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他苦口婆心地和我說人生苦短
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.43,0:33:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道很老土
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.56,0:33:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我媽剛過世
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.16,0:33:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近一直在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.20,0:33:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話  我一直愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.64,0:33:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.25,0:34:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.06,0:34:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親過世我感到很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.97,0:34:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親的事我也很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.63,0:34:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  她也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.67,0:34:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  我來告訴大家她去了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.03,0:34:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}西伯利亞某地
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.24,0:34:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}媽媽來了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.79,0:34:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三胞胎之一
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.47,0:34:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能說是從肥皂劇里抄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.83,0:34:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回到這里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.26,0:34:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了  我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.46,0:34:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你準備好結婚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.17,0:34:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:34:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.48,0:35:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我一直在告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂劇通常以婚禮收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.35,0:35:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了一段漫長之旅后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.14,0:35:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終于開始自己的旅程了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.52,0:35:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.00,0:35:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得注意的是  在這美好的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.67,0:35:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡的激動之情包括了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.63,0:36:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.73,0:36:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.25,0:36:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤芝士三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.67,0:36:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫作
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐爾·索拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.60,0:36:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家今天賞光出席
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.24,0:36:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  我們精選了《愛是你我》的一段話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.32,0:36:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛是你  愛是我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.82,0:36:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我會隨著你一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.45,0:36:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在旁  天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.91,0:36:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猶如幸福加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.57,0:37:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛很歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無拘無束  愛能讓人隨心而動
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.91,0:37:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你念這么大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.87,0:37:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和曾祖木一起練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.43,0:37:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說我很適合做配音
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聲明  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.03,0:37:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我自己這么說可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.64,0:37:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的話我要用西班牙語說
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.11,0:37:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們中有人不懂西班牙語
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.48,0:37:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在手冊中有翻譯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.47,0:37:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我們今天聚在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.04,0:37:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}見證我深愛的外孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.13,0:37:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}簡·格洛瑞娜·維蘭紐瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.02,0:37:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}嫁給拉斐爾·索拉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.62,0:37:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我也非常愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.12,0:37:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}他唯一的缺點是
