Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.62,0:38:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你們讓我知道  這句話很正確
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}因為你們一路走來  風雨波折  就像電視劇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.00,0:38:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.15,0:38:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你們為彼此而戰
