Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.65,0:39:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把這個套在你們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.34,0:39:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象征著合一和承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.59,0:39:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你們之間
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.75,0:39:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠緊密相連了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.12,0:39:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.65,0:39:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.36,0:39:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.26,0:39:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.26,0:39:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}現在你們可以交換結婚誓言了
