Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.10,0:39:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.86,0:39:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.81,0:40:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐爾  我們第一次見面時
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告訴我要勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.98,0:40:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.29,0:40:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐爾
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.97,0:40:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們應該...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  沒錯  -抱歉  我們要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.26,0:40:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-自己讀一下  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.34,0:40:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.34,0:40:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.88,0:40:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}現在還沒到時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.88,0:40:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉  抱歉  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.38,0:40:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}那我快一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}戒指呢
