Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.94,0:41:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐爾  請接受這枚象征著愛和忠誠的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.76,0:41:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.51,0:41:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抱歉  -簡
