Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.07,0:41:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請接受這枚象征著愛和忠誠的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.27,0:41:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.88,0:41:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}別親了  再等三十秒
